Qe3 Rad8 20. Bf1 Qa5 21. hxg6 hxg6 22. Ng5 Bxg5 23. Bxg5 Rxe5 24. Bxd8 Qxd8 25.
Qg3 $14 {Black does not have full compensation for the sacrificed exchange.})
18... Bf8 19. Bg3 ({The way to achieve a considerable advantage was} 19. Ne4 $1
Be7 (19... Bg7 20. h6 Bxe5 21. Nf6+ Kh8 22. Bg5 Bh2+ 23. Kh1 Bf4 24. Qg4 Bxg5
25. Qxg5 Qe5 26. f4 Qxg5 27. fxg5 Na5 28. Be4 $16 {[%csl Rh8] And Black won't
